Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:42.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:45.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,a bit close, Petra?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:48.32,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she had you all to herself earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:49.90,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:50.74,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:53.87,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's not like that, Petra-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:55.39,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru and I were just...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.78,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Right! We had important things to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:02.70,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose to you! You hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:07.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-tan, she's only a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:11.09,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to smile and \Nlaugh off what kids say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:12.08,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:14.57,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:17.12,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take such a lackadaisical attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:19.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Lackadaisical? Who says \Nthat in this day and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:22.85,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You're teasing me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:25.31,Default,Petra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:27.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:30.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I need to thank you, Petra.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:36.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You kept your promise to not \Nleave Emilia-tan alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:41.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people I need \Nto thank when things calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful to Crusch-san and her gang,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:47.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and Anastasia-san and her \Npeople helped a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:49.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And I hate to admit it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:51.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but the same goes for Julius and those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:56.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even indebted to Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:59.04,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something, Natsuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:04.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just that I'm super grateful to you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:07.26,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what brought that on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:08.75,Default,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,You're making me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:09.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:16.19,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:20.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-tan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:26.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There's something really \Nimportant I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:28.62,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:33.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is really hard for me to \Nsay, but please hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:38.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and of course, I'm prepared to be \Nknocked out by Ram when I tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:41.39,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I want you to hear it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:42.46,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:47.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's actually... about Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem said that she, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.57,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You'll still keep me by your side from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:58.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You see what I'm getting at, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:03.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, well... Rem said \Nsome nice things to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.27,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, just calm down for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:08.65,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what you're trying to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.92,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but I can tell you're trying \Nyour hardest to say it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.18,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,So just take it slow, like a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:18.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,"Like a good boy"? That's not\N exactly encouraging.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:20.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But... okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:25.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna come out and say it, like a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:26.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:33.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem said she loves me, the same way \NI told you that I love you! So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:46.58,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:48.16,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.50,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.18,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,is Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:38.28,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look very happy, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.09,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:43.01,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:47.97,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Felis and Wilhelm, and all the volunteers \Nfighting alongside us, are the best of the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:51.49,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Ricardo and the Iron Fang are \Nlending us their aid, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.45,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Such an assembly cannot lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:58.48,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Is it selfish of me to worry despite all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.34,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,It's as Natsuki Subaru said...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:06.98,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,You look best when you're smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.29,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:17.33,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,That Subaru-kun is such a troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:23.44,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you would also look \Nquite different with a smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:26.31,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,since you always carry \Nyourself with such dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.38,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you would look lovely if you smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.85,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.18,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not very good at smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:39.44,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,It is something I still regret, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.12,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.42,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.10,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Run him over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.43,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:28.69,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.72,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,Ordering them to run me over \Nwhen I'm not doing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:35.38,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something any \Ndecent human being would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.30,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do such a brutal \Nthing to my retainers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:41.71,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.22,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.10,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.05,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,But I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:53.35,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,You're a candidate to be the \Nnext ruler of this nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.56,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,You talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:57.02,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.10,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.86,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's just mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:07.56,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,But I suppose one could never hope to rule \Na country without some degree of arrogance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:11.20,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,I can't comprehend that \Nsensibility myself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:12.05,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I told you there would be no second chances!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.34,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,Now, look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:21.16,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,Who taught you that it was acceptable \Nto swing a sword at someone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:23.36,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,when they're happily talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:27.88,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,I do believe that's a violation \Nof my right to speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.21,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.13,Default - flashback,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Felis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.10,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:45.24,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,I keep eating and eating, \Nbut it's never enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:53.19,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,I eat, I devour, I chew, I bite, \NI gorge, I gnaw, I munch, I crunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:55.47,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,Pure gluttony!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:58.69,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, thank you for this feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.83,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You two are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:11.88,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,Sin Archbishop of the Witch's Cult,\N representing gluttony...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.26,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,Lye Batenkaitos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:18.85,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,And the Sin Archbishop of the \NWitch's Cult, representing greed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.23,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,Regulus Corneas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:25.23,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,We came here because we heard \Nour pet had been slain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.90,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,and look at this bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:31.63,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,I expected them to be a good, ripe bunch, \Nconsidering they managed to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:36.49,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,a beast that had been rampaging \Nunchecked for 400 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.28,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,But this is beyond my expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:46.00,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Good! Great! Excellent! Fine! \NPerfect! Fantastic! Stupendous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.25,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,How long it has been since our \Nhunger was so thoroughly sated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:54.09,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,You can relax. I'm nothing \Nlike that guy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.09,0:08:56.50,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,I hate fighting and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:59.00,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,All that "hunger" and "thirst" nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:02.02,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,Such petty self-indulgences are beneath me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.12,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,Were you even listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:11.70,Default - flashback,Regulus,0000,0000,0000,,Did I not just say that I hate fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.80,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you wish to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.36,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,witch cultist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:24.90,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Soon enough, a hero will appear \Nand rid us of all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:30.25,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The one and only hero... whom I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:34.58,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A hero? I look forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.05,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:41.09,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,The head maid of the mansion of \NMargrave Roswaal L. Mathers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.73,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,and currently, the caretaker \Nof my one and only love,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:51.61,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,my beloved Natsuki Subaru, \Nwho will one day be that hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:52.80,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:09:59.66,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be ready, Sin Archbishop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.58,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you, my hero will soon be here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.53,Default - flashback,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,to bring you to justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.55,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what mettle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:19.26,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,I am most certainly going to enjoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.82,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,this feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:49.04,Default - flashback,Ley,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.20,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,How awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:07.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:16.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:18.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Rem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:24.87,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.84,Default - flashback,Otto,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:28.50,Default - flashback,Ram,0000,0000,0000,,I have no younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.45,Default - flashback,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.98,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the time when the White Whale got Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:37.12,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I know we defeated the White Whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.30,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:43.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you hear me, say something, Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.84,0:11:46.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:53.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Not her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:54.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:55.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem! Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.23,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem! Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem! Rem! Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:10.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:15.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:27.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Rem, wake up! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:29.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem... Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.96,0:12:33.33,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,You know this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.89,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! She's Rem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive, right?! Why won't she wake up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:40.49,Default,Healer,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, she's beyond help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.57,Default,Healer,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing I can do will wake her—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! And you call yourself a healer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:47.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a healer, then heal her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wake her up with magic! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:51.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:56.97,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If I Return by Death now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:29.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to fight Petelgeuse again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight him as many times as it takes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:38.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,beat him as many times as it takes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:42.22,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,to save both Emilia and Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let either of them die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If it'll save both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.78,0:13:53.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,As many times as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.40,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.15,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:04.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.80,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:14.98,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.04,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,is Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:29.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:33.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I never really saw you sleeping before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:37.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You always woke up before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Before I realized it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were already in my room,\N watching me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.26,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:47.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to sound all brave,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:53.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,saying I'd die as many times as \Nit would take to save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:57.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess no matter how many times I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:08.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just you, Puck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.49,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,"Just" me? I don't think that was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.95,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:15.60,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So what brings you all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:18.88,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I have a connection with \Nthis girl too, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:22.56,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,So what's wrong with me dropping \Nby to check in on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Puck, couldn't you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:30.84,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but not even my power can \Nwake her from the sleep she's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:36.41,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,It might not do much to make up for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:39.56,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,but I could tell you a bit about Gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:40.54,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:45.00,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,The one who devoured her name and memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.24,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Put simply, the Authority of Gluttony
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.20,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,is a power for eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:55.25,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,He can eat someone's name and \Nmake everyone forget about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:58.88,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,or make that person lose their \Nown memories by eating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.60,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,If both your name and your memories are taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:05.21,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,there'll be nothing left \Nof you but an empty shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:08.33,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happened to this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:10.87,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.38,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:16.48,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to ask a favor of you when you've \Nalready got so much on your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.44,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm counting on you to take care of Lia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:32.30,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.30,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.20,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No changes at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:39.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if there's anything I can even do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:43.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm weak and pathetic, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.01,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:48.90,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you made her quite happy, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:53.82,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... That was crossing a line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:56.09,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I've made you upset, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:56.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, were you looking for me \Nbecause you needed something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:05.96,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Everyone has gathered in \Nthe lounge to discuss things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.22,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,And, well... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:15.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's Natsuki Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:18.86,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Of course, \Nyou're Natsuki Subaru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:21.25,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I've been told that I owe you a great deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:23.81,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,and yet I've been nothing but rude.\N Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, you can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:29.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know you have a lot to remember right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't bother me, Crusch-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:36.85,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-sama, I'm sorry for making \Nyou deliver that message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.53,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's quite all right, Felis-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.24,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,It's just "Felis."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:44.30,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,You and I have known each other for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:47.99,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sad when you talk \Nto me like you don't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:49.20,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:54.88,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I know it won't be like before, \Nbut I'll try my best, Felis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:57.80,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:01.36,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be on your side, Crusch-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:05.77,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's like I'm seeing \Na whole new side to you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.46,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:12.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I've calmed down now, Emilia-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:14.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:18.54,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that Subaru-dono and \NCrusch-sama have returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.12,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,let us talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:24.04,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start by reviewing \Nwhere we currently stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.41,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,By the time the Iron Fang \Nmembers who got away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:29.03,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,brought back reinforcements \Nfrom the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:31.59,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,the only ones left were the casualties and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.51,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,...those in situations similar to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:38.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-san's memories were eaten,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:42.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,and Rem lost both her name and her memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:44.53,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,The capital has also had many cases
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:48.92,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,of memory loss that no healer \Ncould fix, like Crusch-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:53.27,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,and an unexplained malady they've \Ndubbed the "Sleeping Beauty disease."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:56.86,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,But now, all of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:01.61,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,...should be considered the \Nwork of the Witch's Cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:06.82,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I meant nothing against you, Crusch-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:10.39,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I do apologize for frightening you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:14.17,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,No, I apologize for being \Nsuch a hopeless master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:18.75,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying my hardest to \Nremember you, as well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:23.56,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,We finally took care of Sloth,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:27.70,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,and now there's another \NSin Archbishop? This really sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:31.13,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the moment Emilia-sama became \Na candidate in the royal selection,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.86,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,we knew the Witch's Cult would get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:38.17,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... it really is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:40.21,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:44.95,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,They're fixated on getting rid \Nof Emilia-sama, the half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.93,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on now is just a tiny part of—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.37,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:51.42,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Give a little more thought to what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:54.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones at fault here are those scumbags!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:57.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put all the blame on the wrong person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hurting your own allies with \Nmisdirected blame isn't gonna help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:04.24,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Coming from you, Subaru-kyun, \Nthat's so much more convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:06.44,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's the difference in experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:07.36,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Felis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.33,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot ignore the comment you just made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.58,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:17.68,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Natsuki Subaru-sama is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:20.52,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,It is crystal clear where \Nthe blame should fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:25.05,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you do not have the \Nright to ridicule someone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who has made a correct statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:30.12,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Crusch-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:34.19,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia-sama, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.21,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,To you, too, Subaru-kyun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:39.78,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. Let's just get back on topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:42.25,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,But just let me say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:47.05,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,About the alliance we spoke of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:52.43,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Can we just scrap that idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:57.64,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:21:00.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,How did all this lead to the subject \Nof dissolving the alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:05.32,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,An alliance is formed when it \Nbenefits all parties involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:09.41,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,You expect us to ally ourselves \Nwith Emilia-sama, the Witch Cult's target?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:14.66,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Can you promise that Crusch-sama \Nwon't be hurt again if we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.83,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.67,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,I am opposed to that opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:24.20,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you be opposed, Old Man Wil?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:26.47,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Look what's happened to Crusch-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:30.42,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,What point is there in continuing to \Nassist Emilia-sama and her friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:35.40,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,With regard to this "Gluttony," \Nthe one who attacked Crusch-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:37.77,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,We may be given an opportunity for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:41.37,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Is that more important than Crusch-sama's life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:42.41,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Felis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:44.62,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is hard on Crusch-sama, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:48.61,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,She has no idea what's going on, \Nshe can't remember anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:51.14,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,So how can you expect her to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:53.38,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right? Isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:57.75,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can do something \Nabout your memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:02.13,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's not enough right now, \NI'll fix this with my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.84,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't put yourself \Nin any more danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:13.14,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Felis, thank you for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.03,0:22:18.45,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, there is simply \Ntoo much I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:23.00,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember a single detail \Nabout who I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:28.61,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure all of you are perplexed as to \Nhow you should interact with me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:33.35,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,But to everyone who still retains their \Nrespect for me despite all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:34.83,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I must express my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.36,0:22:41.48,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Felis, I know that your \Nconcern for me is genuine,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:44.59,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,and that you are trying to guide me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:49.48,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I could do as you say and walk \Nthe path that is safest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:54.48,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,But I loathe the thought of going \Non with my life, knowing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.48,0:22:58.94,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,If I have a choice, I would \Nrather choose for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.42,0:23:01.32,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,than simply do as someone says.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:12.15,Default,Felis,0000,0000,0000,,Crusch-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.61,0:23:21.50,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Felis...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:37.88,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,If this is Crusch-sama's will,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:40.56,Default,Wilhelm,0000,0000,0000,,surely no one would be in favor \Nof dissolving the alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.09,0:23:42.06,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.06,0:23:46.77,Default,Crusch,0000,0000,0000,,I know I will be a great deal of trouble to \Nyou, Emilia-sama and Natsuki Subaru-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.67,0:23:52.98,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,We can't exactly say we're all \Non the same page, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:23:56.44,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,We need to rejoin Ram and everyone\Nelse who's at the Sanctuary,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:59.52,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,and we need to talk it over with Roswaal, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.46,0:24:14.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You said I was strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.03,0:24:16.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,but without you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:22.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even find the Subaru who \Ncould put on that tough guy act, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:25.16,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.88,0:24:29.53,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.22,0:24:31.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:34.95,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not allowed to be here if I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.93,0:24:39.99,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I know this girl... Rem-san, too, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.57,0:24:42.86,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,"Rem-san," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.51,0:24:44.45,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.28,0:24:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just called her "Rem" before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.06,0:24:51.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're basically Roswaal's guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.37,0:24:55.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to explain that \Nshe's Ram's sister, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.68,0:24:57.63,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.63,0:25:00.03,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,She looks just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.03,0:25:02.14,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistaking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.95,0:25:05.67,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, you haven't slept at all, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.40,0:25:08.15,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.76,0:25:12.15,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm doing anything \Nthat'd make me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.01,0:25:14.74,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I {\i1}can{\i0} do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.74,0:25:18.30,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true that you want \Nto do something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.30,0:25:21.58,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If your spirit keeps trying \Nso hard for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:24.36,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,your body will wear out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.36,0:25:26.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,So... please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.83,0:25:31.43,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.83,0:25:33.84,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.22,0:25:37.50,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You've helped me so much, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.23,0:25:39.52,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I really mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.75,0:25:42.28,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all be fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.00,0:25:46.30,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I have any right \Nto talk as if I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.78,0:25:50.19,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I want to understand how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.40,0:25:55.52,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,but since I don't remember \Nanything about this girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.52,0:25:58.12,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I know anything I say will just hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.17,0:26:02.89,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.54,0:26:05.62,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Just know this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.51,0:26:10.95,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't burden yourself with carrying \Nthe weight of Rem alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.95,0:26:15.03,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Let me carry your burdens with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.90,0:26:17.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.37,0:26:22.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't even remember \Nanything about Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.60,0:26:26.62,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Is it wrong to want to do something \Nif I don't remember her?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.62,0:26:31.51,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,She's important enough to you that \Nit's made you this sad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.06,0:26:37.01,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Is it so strange that it makes \Nme want to help her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.45,0:26:40.53,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you saved me,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.77,0:26:43.72,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I want to save you this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.72,0:26:47.23,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in pain, I want \Nto do something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.37,0:27:01.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Emilia-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.24,0:27:06.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I think you're much \Nmore amazing than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.76,0:27:09.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm really not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.10,0:27:12.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.10,0:27:21.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia... I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.65,0:27:23.45,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.76,0:27:26.50,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Could you turn around?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.56,0:27:28.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.92,0:27:31.86,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.99,0:28:20.61,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.22,0:28:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.74,0:28:24.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.06,0:28:28.00,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.85,0:28:31.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Your hero is going to come for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.68,0:28:33.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.58,0:28:36.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.02,0:28:40.03,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\t(1,3010,\fs24)}Each One's {\c&HF5D8B0&}Promise
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.78,0:28:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rem.
